06:35.580 --> 06:36.990
She was starting a new life.

06:38.290 --> 06:40.667
Hey, you guys, check this out.

06:45.380 --> 06:47.496
The cops' theory is that she was home.

06:47.500 --> 06:50.116
That the UnSub broke in through
the front window and surprised her.

06:50.120 --> 06:53.453
But, look,
this is the gunshot to the chest.

06:53.460 --> 06:55.826
