14:24.420 --> 14:26.661
Acquittals? No.

14:26.670 --> 14:30.208
-Why is it important?
-Because we have a new profile.

14:33.290 --> 14:35.611
We now believe these killings
aren't random.

14:35.620 --> 14:38.453
We might be dealing with a vigilante.

14:38.460 --> 14:42.248
UnSub first shoots his victims
in order to subdue them.

14:42.250 --> 14:47.916
